        "subject": "Fix race conditions related with statahead",
        "message": "Fix race conditions related with statahead\n\n1) race between statahead readdir and other normal readdir for the same\n   directory, maybe cause readdir failure.\n2) race between statahead lookup and create family operations, maybe cause\n   two different dentries with same name pointing to the same inode.\n\nIssue: ORNL-7\nChange-Id: Iee36680df935eba6f3c41acbb1d0a439089d3eaf\n"
      },
